# Xavfsizlik checklist

## Har bir PR

- [ ] Maxfiy ma'lumotlar (`.env`, parollar, tokenlar) commit qilinmagan
- [ ] Yangi API marshrutlari RBAC guard bilan (`route-permission-guard.ts`)
- [ ] Raw SQL: faqat `Prisma.sql` — `queryRawUnsafe` yo'q
- [ ] Input validatsiya: Zod schema (`contracts/`)
- [ ] Rate limit write API uchun (`writeApiRateLimitRouteOpts`)

## Production deploy

- [ ] `RBAC_ENFORCE_PERMISSIONS=1`
- [ ] `CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS` aniq ro'yxat (wildcard yo'q)
- [ ] JWT secrets ≥ 32 belgi, default emas
- [ ] `INTERNAL_HEALTH_TOKEN` — `/ready` va `/metrics`
- [ ] `npm run backup:pre-release` bajarilgan
- [ ] Migratsiya: `npm run db:deploy`

## Monitoring

- [ ] Sentry DSN (ixtiyoriy) yoki log shipping
- [ ] Uptime: `/health` tashqi monitor
- [ ] Grafana alert qoidalari yangilangan (kerak bo'lsa)

## Frontend / Mobile

- [ ] Auth cookie: `SameSite=Strict`, HTTPS da `Secure`
- [ ] Mobile: `.env.local` repoda yo'q
- [ ] APK/foto upload limitlari tekshirilgan

## Tekshiruv buyruqlari

```bash
cd backend && npm run prod:verify
cd backend && npm run build
```

TruffleHog: CI `secret-scan` job.
